        <name>ART: An ontology-based article preparation tool</name>

        <shortdesc xml:lang="en">The project will develop a tool, ART, based on a generic ontology of experiments,EXPO, to assist in; translating scientific papers into format with an explicit semantics, explicit linking of repository papers to data and metadata and the creation of an example intelligent digital repository</shortdesc>

        <description xml:lang="en">The proposal is to use the semantically rich and the theoretically sound generic EXPO representation of scientific experiments to provide metadata and to annotate papers stored in digital repositories. An ontology-based tool, ART, will be developed to automate the process of translating the papers into the proposed semantic format</description>

